{"tid":1755772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家政府玩緊懶理政策！和理非大遊行+SET DEADLINE，咁就名正言順開佢波啦！","createTime":"2019-11-25T18:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T22:41:07.000Z","uid":4875,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"be4faf59de195850bafb3169c261fe750f43b22b","tid":1755772,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:02:28.000Z","msg":"有部份連登仔開始覺得要停停，但唔怪得佢地<br />\n因為其實塞鐵塞+塞路阻人翻工，的確效果已經唔高<br />\n（阻唔耐，手冒比人打風險）<br />\n<br />\n亦有一班人覺得要繼續，迫呢個政府正面回應<br />\n（的確強硬手段先逼到市民關注同政府要回應）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但咁多位手足，唔好唔記得有SET DEADLINE 呢招！<br />\n今日開始全部同我洗版，要求民陣星期日大遊行！<br />\n民間記者會再SET DEADLINE！限期一過就塞佢老母！</span></span>"},{"pid":"44d8b8afcf2ecba14f66ed1350873e5846e337f9","tid":1755772,"uid":4875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:04:50.000Z","msg":"而呢個星期塞唔塞，就由咁多位手足自行決定！<br />\n畢竟呢場遊動有個口號「兄弟覺山，各自努力」<br />\n就算有反效果，都不割席，不指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c90938f723f7e74dd470d30ba565e1bafc5c443","tid":1755772,"uid":36808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:05:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下家長車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"},{"pid":"6d62795a548dd6089e7521c6c0b72e8b51c93b45","tid":1755772,"uid":61160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"支持set deadline唔支持塞鐵塞路<br />\n利申我唔介意塞鐵塞路"},{"pid":"97ddf9799b5f2ad078cf9a1aba5c05feaf68b188","tid":1755772,"uid":34