r: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我地未贏 抗爭繼續 直到香港重光！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請保持憤怒 永遠記住俾人到谷底感覺 驕兵必敗<br />\n同時保持獨立批判思考<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtmbVr0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtmbVr0.jpg&h=6909edf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a11d688fbc9585c1f96cd8d5b16a92aa696a5d7c","tid":1755772,"uid":293595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"Set deadline <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5986338a100231d0fe10d806c6e31f631de6393c","tid":1755772,"uid":4875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1508c28f34ffa4340beb8c1ad662fb286ba79d3c","tid":1755772,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"我唔太讚成set deadline<br />\n太急於求成逼自己升級<br />\n我認為應該繼續現有行動<br />\n直到行動冷卻<br />\n再變招，黃圈建設可加強<br />\n不應隨便升級<br />\n亂升級好易會一Q清袋<br />\n我自己就做好準備長時間抗爭<br />\n目標係攬炒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:19:10.000Z","msg":"無話升級，只係想出師有名！將個波射比政府！<br />\n<br />\n逼到政府回應，只有罷工一條路，但你睇上一個星期就知根本無可能，因此黎明行動係唯一選擇，達到癱瘓效果！<br />\n<br />\n但鑑於上星期黎明行動，的的確確係有小小失民心，呢個係無可厚非。而且長期黎明只係令效果越黎越小！<br />\n<br />\n因此大遊行，再SET DEADLINE，限期一過先塞係現有最好辦法，完完全全掉個波比政府。當然你會問黎明行動政府都唔回應咁點？呢個就只有見步行步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 如果有手足都係覺得立即啟動黎明行動，呢個我都唔會反對，畢竟本著「兄弟爬山，各自努力」，場運動先行到呢步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631509c11003eb10ff0aa4cb8841e08e98689356","tid":1755772,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cb27cfc63aeab10b72e926b037f90bc08a1871","tid":1755772,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:27:39.000Z","msg":"大遊行大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23bc580d38cb3a79f0bc9c5a3518aef25d8f0f0","tid":1755772,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b50eb547ce9c8b645ed2dd5466dd9bbd22a61b","tid":1755772,"uid":61160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ab11e2b8a5fba0077046e70fdb4777da801108b","tid":1755772,"uid":4875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d62795a548dd6089e7521c6c0b72e8b51c93b45","tid":1755772,"uid":61160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"支持set deadline唔支持塞鐵塞路<br />\n利申我唔介意塞鐵塞路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:07:01.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c